{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782298944651,"sessionID":"ses_106b70cc2ffeQ7z094Vd8ASez1","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_l4YejLBEJEf8eI5e5ducwEIB","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"path":"D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie","pattern":"patch_authority.py","include":"*.md"},"output":"Found 1 matches\nD:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\docs\\unified-cangjie-translation-workflow.zh.md:\n  Line 84: `source-coverage-matrix.json` 和 `platform-capability-check.json` 虽然仍是 agent 维护的权威文件，但大批量或关键字段更新应优先通过 `scripts/shared/source_coverage/patch_authority.py` 执行。该工具读取严格 JSON patch payload，通过 `featureId` / `capabilityId` 定位行，支持 `set`、`append`、`remove` 和少量新增行，并在写回前校验字段白名单、status/parity 一致性、critical/high 必填证据、deferred blocker/fallback/future path，以及 active entries 的重复 id。工具写回 JSON 后会直接同步对应 Markdown mirror，避免 agent 临时拼超长 shell 或整文件重写时造成 JSON 失败、字段漂移、Markdown 与 authority 不一致。\n","metadata":{"matches":1,"truncated":false},"title":"patch_authority.py","time":{"start":1782298941083,"end":1782298944650}},"id":"prt_ef94b9677001EMbPrDqKQLlcr3","sessionID":"ses_106b70cc2ffeQ7z094Vd8ASez1","messageID":"msg_ef94b3cd1001zeNgmn7NhosZvn"}}
