\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\tools\\cj-unpacking-tool\\.overview.md:\n  Line 24: This subdirectory functions as the central hub for the complete technical documentation of the OpenHarmony application unpacking tool. It provides an extensive collection of resources that cover Java interface definitions, detailed command-line operation guides, and rigorous data structure specifications. The core functionality described within these documents revolves around the parsing, decompression, and extraction of configuration data from various package formats, including HAP, HSP, and standard App packages. Furthermore, the documentation outlines support for multiple parsing modes and offers critical explanations regarding specific limitations encountered when operating within the Cangjie language environment. These materials are meticulously curated for application market developers, system framework integrators, and developers tasked with debugging or analyzing application packages. The ultimate goal is to provide a holistic technical reference that bridges the gap between low-level underlying interfaces and high-level specific operational procedures, facilitating a deeper understanding of the package lifecycle in the OpenHarmony ecosystem.\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\tools\\cj-restool\\restool工具\\restool工具_2more_e97a69b4.md:\n  Line 11: restool是一种应用工程资源编译工具，通过编译资源文件创建资源索引、解析资源，开发者可以调用[资源管理接口](../reference/LocalizationKit/cj-apis-resource_manager.md)获取到对应资源。restool工具保存在sdk安装目录下的toolchains子目录。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\tools\\cj-restool\\restool工具\\.overview.md:\n  Line 17: 本文档介绍了restool工具，一种用于编译应用工程资源的工具，旨在创建资源索引并解析资源。文档涵盖简介部分，说明了工具的功能、位于SDK toolchains子目录的路径及其与资源管理接口的关联。关键点在于restool通过编译生成索引，开发者可调用资源管理接口获取资源，且该工具目前处于Beta阶段。文档面向SDK应用开发者，属于工具参考类文档，适用于资源编译与管理场景。\r\n\n  Line 20: 这份文档旨在指导开发者使用restool命令行工具进行应用资源管理。