and-line parameters.\r\n\n  Line 22: The core content of the documentation focuses on several key technical areas. These include resource full and incremental compilation, which allows developers to optimize build processes by only recompiling changed resources. It also covers fixed resource ID configuration, which is essential for maintaining consistent resource references across builds. Additionally, the documentation details filtering compilation rules for different device attributes, enabling tailored resource packages for specific hardware. The tool is currently in the Beta stage and is primarily oriented towards SDK application developers and HarmonyOS development personnel. Its ultimate goal is to assist users in efficiently managing application resources and accurately configuring compilation options to meet their project requirements.\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\tools\\cj-packing-tool\\打包工具\\打包工具_3more_1dceed77.md:\n  Line 35:     java -jar app_packing_tool.jar --mode hap --json-path <path> [--resources-path <path>] [--ets-path <path>] [--index-path <path>] [--pack-info-path <path>] [--lib-path <path>] --out-path <path> [--force true] [--compress-level 5] [--pkg-context-path <path>] [--hnp-path <path>]\r\n\n  Line 49: | --resources-path | 否  | NA | resources资源包路径。| NA  |\r\n\n  Line 50: | --index-path  | 否  | NA | .index文件路径，文件名必须为resources.index。| NA |\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\tools\\cj-packing-tool\\打包工具\\多工程打包指令_3more_79bb8523.md:\n  Line 36: java -jar app_packing_tool.jar --mode hqf --json-path <path> [--lib-path <path>] [--ets-path <path>] [--resources-path <path>] --out-path <path> [--force true]\r\n\n  Line 47: | --resources-path  | 否     | NA | resources资源包路径。   |\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\tools\\cj-packing-tool\\打包工具\\HSP打包指令_