geGenerator提取视频指定时间图像\\.overview.md:\n  Line 16: 本文档旨在演示如何使用仓颉语言和MediaKit提取视频指定时间的缩略图。文档包含index.cj和main_ability.cj两个文件，重点展示了UI组件构建、资源管理器获取视频文件描述符以及AVImageGenerator的配置与调用。核心流程包括创建AVImageGenerator对象、设置fdSrc属性、定义PixelMapParams参数、调用fetchFrameByTime获取帧数据，并最终在Image组件中显示。该示例适合熟悉ArkUI框架的开发者，作为实现视频处理功能的参考教程。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\media\\media\\cj-avimagegenerator\\.overview.md:\n  Line 11: *   How to manage video resources using `ResourceManager` or sandbox paths? → Go to [1]\r\n\n  Line 18: This subdirectory offers a detailed guide on the process of extracting thumbnails from video resources at designated times using `AVImageGenerator`. The content is structured to walk developers through a complete development cycle, ensuring no step is overlooked. It starts by explaining how to create an instance of the generator and how to properly configure the file descriptor (`fdSrc`) to point to the video source. The guide then provides specific instructions on invoking the `fetchFrameByTime` method to capture `PixelMap` images corresponding to the requested timestamps. Beyond the extraction logic, it thoroughly covers resource configuration, illustrating how to set up video sources via `ResourceManager` or application sandbox paths. Crucially, it includes steps for resource release to prevent memory leaks. The directory is enriched with complete, executable code examples based on the Cangjie language and MediaKit, serving as a practical reference for developers aiming to master video frame extraction and integrate it seamlessly into their applications. By following these examples, developers can ensure efficient memory usage and high-performance image rendering within their software solutions.\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\media\\image\\cj-image-encoding\\使用ImagePacker完成图片编码\\开发步骤.md:\n  Line 82: // 获取resourceManager资源管理器。\r\n\n  Line 111: