t-input-textinput\\TextInput\\组件属性\\.overview.md:\n  Line 23: 本文档提供了ArkUI框架中使用Cangjie语言设置文本输入组件样式的API参考。主要包含两个函数接口：`style`用于定义文本输入样式，`textAlign`用于设置文本的水平对齐方式。关键信息包括这两个函数均返回`This`以支持链式调用。`style`函数接受`TextInputStyle`枚举参数，默认值为Default；`textAlign`函数接受`TextAlign`枚举参数，默认值为Start。两者均系统能力为ArkUI.Full，起始版本为22。面向使用Cangjie语言开发ArkUI应用的开发者，旨在帮助其自定义文本输入框的外观和布局。\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-text-input-textinput\\TextInput\\基础类型定义_2more_3de06505.md:\n  Line 3: ### class TextInputController\r\n\n  Line 6: public class TextInputController {\r\n\n  Line 11: **功能：** TextInputController是TextInput组件的控制器，可以定义该类型的对象并绑定至TextInput组件，实现对TextInput组件的控制。\r\n\n  Line 23: **功能：** TextInputController的构造函数。\r\n\n  Line 94:     var controller: TextInputController = TextInputController()\r\n\n  Line 98:         TextInput(text: this.text, placeholder: 'input your word...', controller: this.controller)\r\n\n  Line 121:         TextInput( text: 'inline style' )\r\n\n  Line 126:             .style(TextInputStyle.Inline)\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-text-input-textinput\\TextInput\\TextInput_5more_08d8d32d.md:\n  Line 1: # TextInput\r\n\n  Line 23: ### init(?ResourceStr, ?ResourceStr, ?TextInputController)\r\n\n  Line 26: public init(placeholder!: ?ResourceStr = None, text!: ?ResourceStr = None, controller!: ?TextInputController = None)\r\n\n  Line 29: **功能：** 创建一个包含占位符文本、当前文本内容和控制器的TextInput对象。\r\n\n  Line 40: |text|?[ResourceStr](./cj-common-types.md#interface-resourcestr)|否|None| **命名参数。** TextInput的当前值。|\r\n\n  Line 41: |controller|?[TextInputController](#class-textinputcontroller)|否|None| **命名参数。** TextInput组件的控制器。|\r\n\n\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\arkui-cj\\cj-text-input-textinput\\.abstract.md:\n  Line 1: This directory serves as a specialized technical resource for the `T